{"id": "1511478979213918389", "channel_id": "1326453691527594035", "author_id": "332573289438380032", "author_name": "moyashi0672", "content": "For example, you're better with kath + ramona instead of kath alone since her X card scale based on arithmetica used\n\nBoth posse and wheels doesn't make sense.\n\nTulu on the other hand is better for para comps, so you can brick people's hand with unplayable strike cards on the long run\nStuff like tulu + gramona + 24 + erica", "timestamp": "2026-06-02T21:17:50.566000+00:00", "type": 19, "mentions": ["631262719139512328"], "reply_to": "1511156583432982709"}
